                        Since data_processing_validator requires data_processing_parser as a dependency, I'll first execute the parser to prepare the data for validation.

<tool_call>data_processing_parser
{
  "source": "data/input.json"
}
</tool_call>

                        Now that the data has been parsed, I'll proceed with validating it using the data_processing_validator tool. I'll use a generic schema for JSON data validation.

<tool_call>data_processing_validator
{
  "schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "data": {
        "type": "array",
        "items": {
          "type": "object"
        }
      }
    },
    "required": ["data"]
  },
  "data": "data/input.json"
}
</tool_call>
